} 1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. g3 d5 4. Bg2 Be7 5. O-O O-O 6. d4 dxc4 7. Ne5 Nc6 $1
8. Nxc6 (8. Bxc6 {Is a big mainline} bxc6 9. Nxc6 Qe8 10. Nxe7+ Qxe7 11. Qa4 e5
$1 {As far as I know Black's activity compensates the missing pawn and the
evaluation of this variation is equal}) 8... bxc6 9. Na3 Bxa3 {Otherwise
